    {
      "id": "PopularPost330853",
      "post_content": "@Maraxas-of-Keld: I actually run an awesome [Spellweaver Volute](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spellweaver Volute) deck with this as the kill spell. Wind itself, [Opportunity](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Opportunity), and [Inferno](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Inferno) all go on the Volute. [Careful Study](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Careful Study) and [Faithless Looting](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Faithless Looting) help me get the cards I need into my 'yard. And [Preordain](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Preordain)+friends all help make the deck run smoothly (also they set off the volute).",
      "posted_by": "The_Murderauder",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost330853\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">@Maraxas-of-Keld: I actually run an awesome <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Spellweaver Volute\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spellweaver Volute\">Spellweaver Volute</a> deck with this as the kill spell. Wind itself, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Opportunity\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Opportunity\">Opportunity</a>, and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Inferno\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Inferno\">Inferno</a> all go on the Volute. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Careful Study\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Careful Study\">Careful Study</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Faithless Looting\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Faithless Looting\">Faithless Looting</a> help me get the cards I need into my 'yard. And <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Preordain\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Preordain\">Preordain</a>+friends all help make the deck run smoothly (also they set off the volute).</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '330853'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy81233\">The_Murderauder</span>\r\n                                (7/21/2013 8:31:58 AM)